"If he's here, then why doesn't he just eat the whole
planet, and be done with it...oh and technically he
hasn't tried to destroy the Matrix yet."

--- robert riley <bustercross365@...> wrote:
> Megatron Revived/ Organics:
>  
> "I most certainly am not joking.  I nearly crashed
> into him when I arrived.  Besides, I have a score to
> settle with him.  He is here to do what he attempted
> years ago: destroy the Autobot Matrix."
>  
> Organics stepped forward as her step brother brought
> the pilot with him.
> "And Unicron has his minions in full force.  They
> managed to take our brother, a most powerful bounty
> hunter.  They took him with them, up there," she
> said, a little sad and point up, to Unicron.
> "WHAT?!?" the clone roared, clinching his fists.  
> Organics rushed to calm the Emperor clone, to some
> avail.
> 
> Kyle Stewart <dewboy30816@...> wrote:
> Fortuneteller's jaw dropped, "UNICRON!!!!  THAT'S
> NOT
> EVEN FUNNY!!!!"  She certainly thought Seer or Deus
> would have informed her if the world-eating-world
> had
> returned.
>

> details?
> 
> --- robert riley <bustercross365@...> wrote:
> > Megatron Revived:
> >  
> > The femme shook the clone's hand.  He noted how
> > small her hand was to his, but he wasn't the
> average

> enough
